# Styling Standards

## TailwindCSS Usage
- Use Tailwind classes for styling
- Avoid inline CSS
- Use class: syntax instead of ternary operators for conditional classes
- Follow mobile-first responsive design approach

## Color System
- Use Tailwind's color palette
- Maintain consistent color usage across components
- Use semantic color names in theme configuration

## Layout
- Use Flexbox and Grid through Tailwind classes
- Implement proper spacing using Tailwind's spacing scale
- Use container classes for consistent width constraints

## Component-Specific Styles
- Group related styles using Tailwind's group modifier
- Use consistent spacing patterns
- Implement hover, focus, and active states

